data.description: This beautiful pool home is one that you don''t want to miss!  It offers everything you could need including 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, a 3 car garage, bonus room, a large open kitchen and family room, and a den- which could be converted into a formal dining room if you prefer.  In addition to this, the owners recently added an impressive saltwater pool which overlooks a large pond and conservation area.  The oversized backyard truly offers a private oasis for entertaining or just relaxing.  Travertine tile surrounds the pool and all of the outdoor seating areas.  Misters were installed on the covered lanai to keep cool on the warmer days and the upgraded hot tub with wifi and blue tooth speakers is included for the cooler weather.  Inside the home you''ll find a long list of upgraded features including a gourmet kitchen with stainless appliances, granite, mosaic tile backsplash, barn doors on the den, crown molding, upgraded security system with cameras, and much more.  Extra landscaping was installed to enhance the tropical feel and the Travertine tiles were continued along the front entry for a lasting first impression.  This home is centrally located just 3 homes down from the community clubhouse and cafe.  You''ll have the convenience of walking to the gym or to the cafe for your morning coffee.  You''ll also have access to the many community parks, playgrounds, trails, events and activities that Waterset has to offer.  Come see why this home is one of a kind!
